{
  "stem": "22582.5",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And in the morning, usually-- usually they-- when they found somebody has grains in the pocket, they would get a lot of beating, you know.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And it happened to me that I got beating on the way back when they find that I have some grain in the thing because we were stealing.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We were there-- we-- the farmers showed us the hospitality, and they were stealing from them.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So we got beating for it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But that's the only way you could survive.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And whoever couldn't walk was just shot.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And all mostly it was taking-- we had a wagon, and the prisoners was pulling the wagon.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And in the evening, they took-- took those people who couldn't walk to the to-- to-- the woods.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "When we're passing whenever they found some woods, and they shot them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Or when people were running away from the-- from the transport during the day, so they shot them on the spot.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "There were some people who escaped and survived somehow, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But-- but most of them, they got killed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They got.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I remember when I had a very good friend, and-- which I escaped later together.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, Schreiber.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Schreiber.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We escaped, and he survived, too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But he died a few a months-- a few years ago.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we had another friend.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were with me and my friend were pulling him, pulling him.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he was a man a head taller than we were.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Bohanek.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Henech Bohanek.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This name I remember.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Henech Bohanek.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was from Krakow.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were pulling him, and we're pulling him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then the guard saw that we were pulling him, and that they were slowing the-- the transport, you know.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
